=== FIRST_CONTACT_LOG ===
# id: 67
# title: The First Contact Log
# chinese_title: 第一次接触
# category: Lore
# mode: dungeon

A heavily encrypted data crystal contains logs from humanity's first verified contact with alien intelligence. The translation is fragmentary but haunting — the aliens spoke of "characters that bind reality" and "radicals of creation." They seemed to already know Chinese.

* [Decrypt and study the full log]
  ~ gain_radical("言")
  "言" (yán) — speech, language, words
* [Copy the crystal for later analysis]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "外" (wài) — outside, foreign, alien
* [Try to trace the aliens' origin coordinates]
  ~ gain_gold(20)
  "源" (yuán) — source, origin
